arChildNodes.szComment: Torben coldly  discusses his knowledge of Blockweald Company.
Torben speaks to desperate folk employing Blackweald Company during desperate times.
A local interrupts Torben's discussion, calling to fires spotten in the south. She is distraught, fearing fires akin to the Days of Ash.
Torben recognizes that Blackweald Company is acting quickly, spreading fires again.
Torben asks the player to look for the fire's source. He believes this is all connected (to Blackweald Company)
Torben declares he will not allow any harm to come to the (Goose) inn.
